<html>
<body>
To configure your Legacy's Dawning environment for optimum playability, use<br>
the various option systems:<br>
 <br>
 Message :: a list of various messages you will get for different<br>
 occurences.<br>
 <br>
 Iflag :: toggles your info messages.  To turn off all messages, just<br>
 type info.<br>
 <br>
 Option :: your options to configure your play.<br>
 <br>
 Color :: you can set your terminal type with this, and associate<br>
 different colours for different events based on your personal<br>
 preference.<br>
</html>
</body>
